    "attributes": {
        "action": "Government to fund a scheme for carers flying with a person with disabilities",
        "additional_details": "These concessions are desperately needed for example  I flew to Australia in 2005 and because I\u2019m 6\u20195 I\u2019m unable to fly economy so I\u2019m forced to fly business or first class, on this occasion I paid for first class seats but I had to provide a equal seat for my carer and the total cost for the flight was \u00a313,000 surely you can see this is totally disgusting.  Just because I\u2019m disabled that doesn\u2019t mean I shouldn\u2019t be able to go on holiday when I want",
        "background": "I\u2019m asking the government to look into possible concessions for carers who have to fly with disabled people,I understand it\u2019s not a governmental problem it\u2019s in it\u2019s a commercial problem but surely there is something you can do",
